1. Install Node.js
Ensure Node.js is installed. Download here.

2. Initialize the Project
Run these commands in your terminal:

npm init -y
npm install express nodemailer axios body-parser


3. Folder Structure
Create the following files in your project folder:

/project-folder
    /public
        index.html
        styles.css
        script.js
    server.js
    db.txt

